<h2>Urgent Help</h2>

If you need support or advice urgently, there are a number of services that you can contact: 
<ul> 
    <li>Your own GP or current health care practitioner</li>
    <li>Your local Accident and Emergency Department</li> 
    <li>Call 999</li>    
    <li>Call NHS 111</li>  
    <li><a target="_blank" href="http://www.samaritans.org/">The Samaritans (24 hours)</a>: Telephone 08457 90 90 90</li>
</ul>

